"Since Motsepe's inception, we wanted to become the agency that will provide a solution to large companies' marketing needs, "said Gee Motsepe, managing director at Motsepe Advertising. "Since then, we've realised that building a business in our already struggling economy is beneficial because it also adds value to the families of the people we employ - which is ultimately the main reason we are in this business". Motsepe Adverting is committed to making a superlative change in the advertising and marketing industry across the world. This through-the-line business-to-business focussed agency aims to help large companies grow their revenue through concentrated effort in digital services. "Our mission is based on four pillars; 1. People – motivated by us being able to create jobs and empower women and youth.  2. Purpose – Creating measurable and successful campaigns for our clients 3. Perception – To be perceived as the defector choice in B2B communication  4. Profit – To yield a profit to enable our mission, purpose, perception and success", adds Boitumelo Motsepe, co-founder and client service director.  B2B being such a niche market, Motsepe's focus and speciality care in the following industries:  1. Banking and Finance 2. Mining and Machinery  3. Logistics and Supply Chain  4. Telecoms and IT 5. Automotive and Engineering  6. Government and Parastatal"We are fortunate to also have a team that believes in the vision of Motsepe Advertising. It's in our DNA to have a can-do attitude. We are a team that constantly innovates, solves, makes a plan, ploughs through and shines," Boitumelo concludes. For more information on Motsepe Advertising, contact:  Managing director – moc.gnisitrevdaepestom@eeg or;  Client service director – moc.gnisitrevdaepestom@olemutiob.